to his and sufficiently removed from the invisible world for his next step. Holding her by the hips, he fed on her half-opened active mouth; she freed herself, fearing that his young impatience might resolve itself too soon; he nuzzled her in her deep soft neck.

“Please,” he murmured, “please, I implore you.”

“Silly,” she said. “Why, of course. But you have to lock the door first.”

